# 雙鑽石模型在創業 一人公司 MVP Lean Startup Personal to Business 應用變體 是否有獨立框架名稱：雙鑽石 Double Diamond 官方定義 經典用法 vs 個人問題到商業化兩階段套用

## 來源列表
1. [The Double Diamond — Design Council](https://www.designcouncil.org.uk/resources/the-double-diamond/) — 官方資源，頁面未標日期，頁尾 ©2026  
2. [Framework for Innovation — Design Council](https://www.designcouncil.org.uk/resources/framework-for-innovation/) — 官方資源，頁面未標日期，頁尾 ©2026  
3. [What is the double diamond model? — Dovetail](https://dovetail.com/design-thinking/double-diamond-model/) — Last updated 2026-04-15  
4. [Design Thinking “Double Diamond” Process — Umbrex](https://umbrex.com/resources/frameworks/organization-frameworks/design-thinking-double-diamond-process/) — 頁面未標日期  
5. [What Is an MVP? Eric Ries Explains — Lean Startup Co.](https://leanstartup.co/resources/articles/what-is-an-mvp/) — 頁面標示原文來自 Startup Lessons Learned，頁面未標日期  
6. [Lean Startup — Lean Enterprise Institute](https://www.lean.org/lexicon-terms/lean-startup/) — 頁面未標日期  
7. [Lean Canvas — Umbrex](https://umbrex.com/resources/frameworks/organization-frameworks/lean-canvas/) — 頁面未標日期  
8. [Scratch Your Own Itch — The Basics Guide](https://thebasics.guide/scratch-your-own-itch/) — 頁面未標日期  
9. [What Is a One-Person Company? — OPC Community](https://www.opc.community/one-person-company) — Updated April 2026  
10. [Personal brand vs. business brand — Cultmethod](https://cultmethod.com/articles/personal-vs-business-brand/) — 頁面未標日期  

## 原文摘錄

### 來源 1
> “A universally accepted depiction of the design process.”

### 來源 2
> “This is not a linear process”

### 來源 3
> “maps how designers move from understanding a problem to delivering a solution.”

### 來源 4
> “build the right thing, not just build quickly.”

### 來源 5
> “maximum amount of validated learning about customers with the least effort”

### 來源 6
> “hypotheses that must be validated by rapid experimentation in the marketplace.”

### 來源 7
> “startup‑oriented adaptation of the Business Model Canvas”

### 來源 8
> “personal frustrations can inspire solutions with wider appeal.”

### 來源 9
> “profitable business operated by a single founder.”

### 來源 10
> “hybrid between the personal brand and the corporate brand.”

## 關鍵重點
- 官方雙鑽石定義仍是設計與創新流程，不是創業商業化專屬框架；核心是 Discover / Define / Develop / Deliver。（來源 1：https://www.designcouncil.org.uk/resources/the-double-diamond/）
- Design Council 官方延伸版強調雙鑽石不是線性流程，會因新理解回到前面階段，這能支撐 MVP / 迭代式驗證的接法。（來源 2：https://www.designcouncil.org.uk/resources/framework-for-innovation/）
- 近期整理型資料把雙鑽石明確描述為「從理解問題到交付解法」的流程，仍屬設計思考、服務設計、產品開發語境。（來源 3：https://dovetail.com/design-thinking/double-diamond-model/）
- 創業 / MVP 語境中，雙鑽石常被拿來補強 Lean / Agile 的前端問題定義，避免只追求快速建置。（來源 4：https://umbrex.com/resources/frameworks/organization-frameworks/design-thinking-double-diamond-process/）
- Lean Startup / MVP 的核心不是「做最小產品」，而是用最小努力取得 validated learning。（來源 5：https://leanstartup.co/resources/articles/what-is-an-mvp/）
- Lean Startup 本身把創業想法視為需被市場實驗驗證的假設，這比雙鑽石更接近商業化驗證語言。（來源 6：https://www.lean.org/lexicon-terms/lean-startup/）
- 「個人問題 → 商業化」若要找較接近的既有框架名稱，查到的是 Lean Canvas、Business Model Canvas、Value Proposition Canvas、Build-Measure-Learn、Scratch Your Own Itch、One-Person Company、Personality-driven business brand；沒有查到一個被廣泛承認、專門叫做「Double Diamond personal-to-business」的獨立框架名稱。（來源 7：https://umbrex.com/resources/frameworks/organization-frameworks/lean-canvas/；來源 8：https://thebasics.guide/scratch-your-own-itch/；來源 9：https://www.opc.community/one-person-company；來源 10：https://cultmethod.com/articles/personal-vs-business-brand/）

## 不確定點
- 無資料：沒有找到「雙鑽石模型 + 一人公司 + 個人問題到商業化兩階段套用」已形成公認獨立框架名稱的來源。
- 無資料：沒有找到 Design Council 官方把 Double Diamond 定義成「個人痛點到商業化」專用創業框架。
- 可追溯的相近命名是 Lean Canvas / Build-Measure-Learn / Scratch Your Own Itch / One-Person Company / personality-driven business brand，但它們是相鄰框架或商業語境，不是雙鑽石官方變體。
